-21","vote_average":7.573,"backdrop_path":"/uqOuJ50EtTj7kkDIXP8LCg7G45D.jpg","original_title":"Ex Machina","original_language":"en"},{"id":297222,"adult":false,"title":"PK","video":false,"overview":"A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, the man's innocent questions and childlike curiosity take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting go.","genre_ids":[35,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4022,"vote_count":1122,"poster_path":"/z2x2Y4tncefsIU7h82gmUM5vnBJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-18","vote_average":7.698,"backdrop_path":"/gxfvtq5eYiClS2X7hxAAPBNrbWA.jpg","original_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":466272,"adult":false,"title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","video":false,"overview":"Los Angeles, 1969. TV star Rick Dalton, a struggling actor specializing in westerns, and stuntman Cliff Booth, his best friend, try to survive in a constantly changing movie industry. Dalton is the neighbor of the young and promising actress and model Sharon Tate, who has just married the prestigious Polish director Roman Polanski…","genre_ids":[35,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.721,"vote_count":14579,"poster_path":"/8j58iEBw9pOXFD2L0nt0ZXeHviB.jpg","release_date":"2019-07-24","vote_average":7.423,"backdrop_path":"/kKTPv9LKKs5L3oO1y5FNObxAPWI.jpg","original_title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","original_language":"en"},{"id":1233413,"adult":false,"title":"Sinners","video":false,"overview":"Trying to leave their troubled lives behind, twin brothers return to their hometown to start again, only to discover that an even greater evil is waiting to welcome them back.","genre_ids":[27,28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":35.9627,"vote_count":3782,"poster_path":"/qTvFWCGeGXgBRaINLY1zqgTPSpn.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-16","vote_average":7.49,"backdrop_path":"/nAxGnGHOsfzufThz20zgmRwKur3.jpg","original_title":"Sinners","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":87,"adult":false,"title":"Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom","video":false,"overview":"After arriving in India, Indiana Jones is asked by a desperate village to find a mystical stone. He agrees – and stumbles upon a secret cult plotting a terrible plan in the catacombs of an ancient palace.","genre_ids":[12,28],"popularity":9.179,"vote_count":9952,"poster_path":"/gpdVNUaa4LhRMLfJOPj1AZdhAZ3.jpg","release_date":"1984-05-23","vote_average":7.304,"backdrop_path":"/f133nWlU6yUkZqqwcCXCbTEJWHr.jpg","original_title":"Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom","original_language":"en"},{"id":1669,"adult":false,"title":"The Hunt for Red October","video":false,"overview":"A new technologically-superior Soviet nuclear sub, the Red October, is heading for the U.S. coast under the command of Captain Marko Ramius. The American government thinks Ramius is planning to attack. Lone CIA analyst Jack Ryan has a different idea: he thinks Ramius is planning to defect, but he has only a few hours to find him and prove it - because the entire Russian naval and air commands are trying to find Ramius, too. The hunt is on!","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":4.1482,"vote_count":3551,"poster_path":"/yVl7zidse4KiWtGMqHFtZCx4X3N.jpg","release_date":"1990-03-02","vote_average":7.379,"backdrop_path":"/5jCpCFrku6wmCZOYZWhHOC2j8IU.jpg","original_title":"The Hunt for Red October","original_language":"en"},{"id":1726,"adult":false,"title":"Iron Man","video":false,"overview":"After being held captive in an Afghan cave, billionaire engineer Tony Stark creates a unique weaponized suit of armor to fight evil.","genre_ids":[28,878,12],"popularity":18.753,"vote_count":27782,"poster_path":"/78lPtwv72eTNqFW9COBYI0dWDJa.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-30","vote_average":7.655,"backdrop_path":"/cKvDv2LpwVEqbdXWoQl4XgGN6le.jpg","original_title":"Iron Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":1991,"adult":false,"title":"Death Proof","video":false,"overview":"Austin's hottest DJ, Jungle Julia, sets out into the night to unwind with her two friends Shanna and Arlene. Covertly tracking their moves is Stuntman Mike, a scarred rebel leering from behind the wheel of his muscle car, revving just feet away.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":3.6374,"vote_count":5511,"poster_path":"/vtu6H4NWnQVqEp3aanUq3hNeeot.jpg","release_date":"2007-05-22","vote_average":6.841,"backdrop_path":"/qbVCChwbGWDAgsCXKZxyjBrRiWx.jpg","original_title":"Death Proof","original_language":"en"},{"id":1949,"adult":false,"title":"Zodiac","video":false,"overview":"Over the course of a decade, editors of the San Francisco Chronicle entice themselves in the murders of the Zodiac Killer. However, as time runs its course, interest in the case dwindles in the eyes of the professionals. The Killer stops interacting with the public. However, believing he has the answers, an amateur cartoonist from the initial sightings races against time to prevent what he believes is another murder.","genre_ids":[80,9648,53],"popularity":8.7043,"vote_count":11350,"poster_path":"/6YmeO4pB7XTh8P8F960O1uA14JO.jpg","release_date":"2007-03-02","vote_average":7.527,"backdrop_path":"/3zCPI4JFc54xvLaJ71oI2KoP3az.jpg","original_title":"Zodiac","original_language":"en"},{"id":2034,"adult":false,"title":"Training Day","video":false,"overview":"On his first day on the job as a narcotics officer, a rookie cop works with a rogue detective who isn't what he appears.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"popularity":6.0322,"vote_count":6443,"poster_path":"/bUeiwBQdupBLQthMCHKV7zv56uv.jpg","release_date":"2001-10-05","vote_average":7.512,"backdrop_path":"/nuO8o9ltxhI7AZQxePavEZ4TyHa.jpg","original_title":"Training Day","original_language":"en"},{"id":273404,"adult":false,"title":"I'll Follow You Down","video":false,"overview":"After the disappearance of a young scientist on a business trip, his son and wife struggle to cope, only to make a bizarre discovery years later - one that may bring him home.","genre_ids":[878,18,9648],"popularity":0.9537,"vote_count":190,"poster_path":"/3osrKXIz5OkSr