 been exhausted by mankind. Battles rage for the remainder between the competing Corporations. During one such battle the seal is broken and awakens an ancient and deadly machine that was once defeated thousands of years ago. The order that awaited its return must now lead a small group of soldiers to destroy it once and for all.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"popularity":1.511,"vote_count":494,"poster_path":"/vHH9VnQZYdhWE9PMMKUpYrG1Z0Z.jpg","release_date":"2008-08-07","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/6gFKEYJ3UugiIm6JUGcoaEDah9M.jpg","original_title":"Mutant Chronicles","original_language":"en"},{"id":13938,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Dragon","video":false,"overview":"A young man searches for the \"master\" to obtain the final level of martial arts mastery known as the glow. Along the way he must fight an evil martial arts expert and rescue a beautiful singer from an obsessed music promoter.","genre_ids":[28,12,10402,35,18],"popularity":2.4752,"vote_count":276,"poster_path":"/r5QnLY30gXlZ8luiJE3quDs1WNF.jpg","release_date":"1985-03-22","vote_average":6.471,"backdrop_path":"/9pqox4KAKGdfqYTkdXeDImUWWmJ.jpg","original_title":"The Last Dragon","original_language":"en"},{"id":8961,"adult":false,"title":"Bad Boys II","video":false,"overview":"Detectives Marcus Burnett and Mike Lowrey of the Miami Narcotics Task Force are tasked with stopping the flow of the drug Ecstasy into Miami. They track the drugs to the whacked-out Cuban drug lord Johnny Tapia, who is also involved in a bloody war with Russian and Haitian mobsters. If that isn't bad enough, there's tension between the two detectives when Marcus discovers that playboy Mike is secretly romancing Marcus’ sister, Syd.","genre_ids":[28,80,35],"popularity":6.4976,"vote_count":5826,"poster_path":"/yCvB5fG5aEPqa1St7ihY6KEAsHD.jpg","release_date":"2003-07-18","vote_average":6.655,"backdrop_path":"/gxSVZCUlDd8upT1G2wdrUdz2hxG.jpg","original_title":"Bad Boys II","original_language":"en"},{"id":9737,"adult":false,"title":"